{"tid":932106,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有圖笑死 推三指手套減用塑膠被指「走火入魔」　KFC：會加強推廣環保訊息","createTime":"2018-12-07T13:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T13:32:49.000Z","uid":121464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"01a66a0e8e791e50d93d70db95cd8facbbe664aa","tid":932106,"uid":121464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T13:09:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/267349/推三指手套減用塑膠被指-走火入魔-kfc-會加強推廣環保訊息\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C%2F267349%2F%E6%8E%A8%E4%B8%89%E6%8C%87%E6%89%8B%E5%A5%97%E6%B8%9B%E7%94%A8%E5%A1%91%E8%86%A0%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87-%E8%B5%B0%E7%81%AB%E5%85%A5%E9%AD%94-kfc-%E6%9C%83%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E6%8E%A8%E5%BB%A3%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF&d=KLjtiXc3fQ3DmHQ9vMEc96EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=05071236\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/267349/推三指手套減用塑膠被指-走火入魔-kfc-會加強推廣環保訊息</a><br />\n<br />\n為響應環保，不少食店推出相關措施，其中連鎖快餐店肯德基（KFC）早前推出了「三指手套」，減少使用塑膠。有連登網民就發文批評「搞乜X，KFC手套得半個」，質疑措施是否「走火入魔」，甚至有網民不知道是新式手套，反問「攞個新囉」，以為是問題產品，甚至有人教路可以「拎埋另一邊」，拿多一隻手套戴在無名指及尾指上。<br />\n香港肯德基回應《香港01》記者指，「三指手套」在其他國家推行後能進一步減廢，對於網民疑問，他們會加強推廣環保訊息及與顧客溝通。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zHkdMEs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzHkdMEs.png&h=93a6e649&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38fc7185de51aef98708945f89ccb1839eda4478","tid":932106,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T13:27:20.000Z","msg":"執晒佢咪最環保囉"},{"pid":"65f136c6f901c683842825b416d9c73f2585c7b9","tid":932106,"uid":48334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T13:28:06.000Z","msg":"無套咪環保"},{"pid":"3f6869b64e40019a028e177ecb21464037ebc230","tid":932106,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T13:30:05.000Z","msg":"拎黎通櫃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},